                      "name": "Отголоски подношения",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4953,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/31/237301566/188a2af60b1978f2e8b627ac5f500c03_3230425734561503487.png",
                      "name": "Чай Адептов",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Archon War",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/15/237301566/6258654267ebf786d39a77b385b2e0ab_7308345604311255648.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "When the Heavenly Principles declared a war for the divine throne and rule of Teyvat, the Master of Fujin and Herblord fought against Rex Lapis. According to Fujin, her lord went mad seeking the position of a god who may rule this world, or she was simply trying to survive, because she understood that she could not defeat Morax. In a desperate attempt to reverse fate, she caused the Bishui River to overflow its banks, destroying everything downstream. Herblord and Fujin could not allow people to die, so they went against their goddess. According to legend, Herblord delayed the goddess with a battle, and Fujin threw the Votive Rainjade into the water, which stopped the river from flooding. Fujin released the Adeptal energy from the Jade Pendant to cause the ground to open up and swallow the Bishui River, allowing the Jademouth to grow and stabilize the flow. Lingyuan summoned her familiars, the Xuanwen beasts, to help her friends and drive the people into the caves. During the war, Fujin spent all her energy and spent many years in Carp's Rest, unable to leave it.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Related Entries:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5118,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/07/237301566/325cbba5840f838320e670c107f49195_2432905045549032697.png",
                      "name": "Долина Чэньюй",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7088,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/12/15/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_3277280826417124317.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Archon War",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7469,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Morax",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5090,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/15/237301566/dd8f5758152aa51a1db8f3f98df320d9_8490048509397913638.png",
                      "name": "Властительница лекарств",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5085,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/15/237301566/5b4231e4ced390bfd124db7badbc7e2a_2633095199288228405.png",
                      "name": "Лин Юань",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5057,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/02/02/70239714/d75494fa72798564617469b6393fac97_7912176143644694059.png",
                      "name": "Зверь Сюаньвэнь",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Chenyu's Blessings of Sunken Jade",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Thousands of years later, the Mountain Lord decided to return Chenyu lands to their state before the arrival of people. She believed that she, and the carps, and snakes all came from nature, so she wanted to return everything to the form that was at their birth. Then the rivers rose and fell with the rains, their paths were not fixed, the tea trees and flowers were not trimmed or cultivated, nor did they exist for humanity. Lingyuan believed that in such an environment, Fujin would regain her true carp form and spiritual strength and frolic in the great rivers. For many years, the Mountain Lord was changing the spirit veins, due to which the soil deteriorated, and a thick fog arose.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/15/237301566/32a53ea6575595c0d13233ec1748138a_3604543691133244023.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Fujin, who cares about the people of the vale, asked for the help of the Traveler to restore the spirit veins and change the soil. The Adeptus did not have enough strength to perform the Rainjade Rite herself, so she needed help. She didn't want Qiaoying Village, famous for its tea, to lose its reason for existence. Thanks to Traveler, Paimon and Lingyuan's friend, Little Mao, Fujin was able to gain enough strength to perform a ritual on the sacred mountain and stop Lingyuan. The Suanni accepted defeat and, for the sake of her friend, agreed not to interfere with caring for people.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "On the Chiwang Terrace, where all the spirit veins of Chenyu Vale converge, Fujin transmitted her Adeptal energy throughout the vale to restore the water and soil. Having spent all her powers during the ritual, she again lost the ability to take human form, but was happy to return her friend and save people.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When the Traveler again helped gather Fujin's power, which had been scattered during the ritual, Fujin decided to visit Guili Plains and Liyue Harbor to look at the people and get to know them. She also wanted to meet with Herblord and convince Lingyuan to go with her.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Related Entries:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5118,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/07/237301566/325cbba5840f838320e670c107f49195_2432905045549032697.png",
                      "name": "Долина Чэньюй",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5549,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/25/41133912/c3b05f550a4a993a64548c995c9ab98c_2384091145152107228.png",
